## هيكل الملفات — Feature CRUD كاملة

```
lib/Features/{feature}/
  ├── domain/
  │   ├── entities/
  │   │   └── {entity}.dart
  │   ├── repositories/
  │   │   └── {feature}_repository.dart
  │   └── usecases/
  │       ├── get_{feature}_list.dart   ← pagination
  │       ├── get_{feature}_detail.dart ← تفاصيل واحد
  │       ├── create_{feature}.dart
  │       ├── update_{feature}.dart
  │       └── delete_{feature}.dart
  ├── data/  ← كالمعتاد (models / datasources / repositories)
  └── presentation/
      ├── cubits/
      │   ├── {feature}_list_cubit.dart   ← extends PaginationCubit
      │   ├── {feature}_form_cubit.dart   ← إضافة + تعديل معاً
      │   └── {feature}_form_state.dart
      └── pages/
          ├── {feature}_list_screen.dart
          ├── {feature}_detail_screen.dart  ← اختياري
          └── {feature}_form_screen.dart    ← إضافة + تعديل
```

